/landing/mobArticle2/id/2297564/%E6%94%9C%E7%A8%8B%E7%B6%B2%E6%96%A524%E5%84%84%E5%85%A5%E8%82%A1TripAdvisor\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2297564%2F%25E6%2594%259C%25E7%25A8%258B%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%2596%25A524%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%2582%25A1TripAdvisor&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=0e12bcd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2297564/%E6%94%9C%E7%A8%8B%E7%B6%B2%E6%96%A524%E5%84%84%E5%85%A5%E8%82%A1TripAdvisor</a><br />\n<br />\n登入 攜程網斥24億入股TripAdvisor"},{"pid":"228d956612c15a15eff7ac6976587d6727f96fb5","tid":1669244,"uid":46161,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T15:25:36.000Z","msg":"旅遊網站TripAdvisor公布，與在美國納斯特上市的中國旅遊網站攜程網(<a href=\"http://Trip.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FTrip.com&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DUy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=430cb18b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Trip.com</a>)建立合夥關係，後者將購入價值3.176億美元(24.77億港元)的TripAdvisor股份，而雙方也會成立合營企業拓展業務。攜程網將派一人成為TripAdvisor董事。<br />\n<br />\n同時，TripAdvisor派發特別股息4.9億美元，相當於每股3.5美元；另增股份回購規模1億美元，至2.5億美元。同時，該公司將評估成本架構。<br />\n<br />\n另外，TripAdvisor公布，第三季利潤按年跌27.5%至5000萬美元；每股經調整盈利58美仙，收入跌6.6%至4.28億美元，分析員預測是69美仙與4.59億美元。<br />\n<br />\n消息公布後，該公司股價在市後時段跌4%。"},{"pid":"7b43c733f8ba04029a0aee30f1e00648727cde6e","tid":1669244,"uid":28353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:12:09.000Z","msg":"skyscanner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a73d34ac4f61794cc9fbba18145e17ea1ed007c","tid":1669244,"uid":135628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:16:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a92e5ff9caaa2dc9684aa87ecbdf56c553f30965","tid":1669244,"uid":82553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:18:37.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"3ceace5827c052b9f2c0e0b